<font color="#FF0000">VIETNAMESE AMERICAN ANTHOLOGY</font><br>
<tt>Thu Jan 23 11:13:29 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
At the end of '97, The Asian American Writers' Workshop (www.panix.com/~aaww) will release WATERMARK: Vietnamese American Poetry &amp; Fiction.  This, believe it or not, will be one of the 1st literary collections by Vietnamese Americans.  The book will emphasize craft over topic &amp; is not limited to the war.  Consider this an introduction to the people.  As we are not-for-profit, donations of any size to support the publication are much appreciated.<br><br>
Please watch for WATERMARK's landmark release.
